    <h1>Setting up processes</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Processes allow you to automate many complex tasks in plentymarkets.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Learn the basics in our playful tutorial:</p>
</div>
<div class="videoblock">
<div class="title">Creating and starting a process</div>
<div class="content">
