<p>Admin users are automatically allowed to access the menu <strong>Setup » Processes</strong>. <strong>Backend</strong> users need to be granted this right. Go to <strong>Setup » Settings » User » Rights » User</strong>. Open the user account. In the <strong>Rights</strong> area, place a check mark next to the menu visibility <strong>Setup » Processes</strong>.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
