<h2 id="65">3. Creating a process</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Processes</strong> to create and manage processes. Proceed as described below to create a process.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Creating a process:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Processes » New process</strong>.<br>
<strong><em>Note:</em></strong> If the menu <strong>Setup » Processes</strong> is not visible, then install the <a href="https://marketplace.plentymarkets.com/en/plugins/integration/plentybase_5053" target="_blank" rel="noopener">plentyBase</a>&nbsp;<span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-external-link  "></i></span> plugin.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the desired settings. Note <a href="#table-process-settings">Table 2</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.<br>
→ The process will appear in the menu tree.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
