<strong>Predefined note</strong> = Opens a window. Enter a message into the Message area. This message will automatically be saved for faulty orders while running the process.<br>
<strong>None</strong> = Neither an individual note nor a predefined note is saved for faulty orders. Use this option if you only want to save the error message as the order note.<br>
<strong>Save error message as additional note</strong> = Place a check mark to save the error message displayed in the process as an order note.</p></td>
</tr>
